edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.nodeconfig

Class GNSConsistentNodeConfig<NodeIDType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.nodeconfig.GNSConsistentNodeConfig<NodeIDType>
  • Type Parameters:
    NodeIDType -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    GNSInterfaceNodeConfig<NodeIDType>, edu.umass.cs.nio.interfaces.NodeConfig<NodeIDType>, edu.umass.cs.nio.interfaces.Stringifiable<NodeIDType>, edu.umass.cs.reconfiguration.interfaces.ReconfigurableNodeConfig<NodeIDType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GNSConsistentReconfigurableNodeConfig

    public class GNSConsistentNodeConfig<NodeIDType>
extends Object
implements GNSInterfaceNodeConfig<NodeIDType>
    A wrapper around NodeConfig to ensure that it is consistent, i.e., it returns consistent results even if it changes midway. In particular, it does not allow the use of a method like getNodeIDs().
